<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-86-1490 </DOCNO><TEXT>The probabilities for photon emission in spontaneous electron transitionsbetween Landau levels in a strong magnetic field B {similar_to} B/subc/ are investigated on the basis of the relativistic quantum expressions.The characteristic time scales for the electron transitions are estimated.The spectra and polarization of quantum synchrotron radiation and stationarysynchrotron cooling radiation are calculated.</TEXT></DOC>